There is still much to learn, but now you can hold a conversation, ask and
answer questions, and ask your partner to help you out. Toki Pona is most
pleasant when you have got someone to enjoy it together with. So go out into the
community, meet new people, make friends!

If you want to combine listening and talking, join a #link("https://bsky.app/profile/tokiponavr.bsky.social")[VRChat] meetup, where people can hang out as virtual avatars! Every Saturday
some Toki Pona speakers and learners come to enjoy our time together, and talk
about things we care about in this nice language.
